sequenceDiagram
    %% Generated: v1.7.0 | 2026-07-14 | ADR-0034 · ADR-0079 · ADR-0084 sweep judge via complete()
    title Review Queue - Create action and auto-resolution sweep - ADR-0034 §5 §6 - sweep LLM judge via complete ADR-0084
    autonumber

    participant U as Web UI
    participant API as FastAPI /review/queue
    participant PG as Postgres
    participant L as run_orchestrated_loop
    participant P as InferenceProvider
    participant FS as Wiki FS
    participant R as ops/review.py (sweep)

    %% Create action
    Note over U,API: User clicks "Create" on a pending proposal (item_type may be any of the five types)
    U->>API: POST /review/queue/{id}/create  (or /approve - same handler)
    API->>PG: SELECT review_items WHERE id=? (404 if absent)
    alt status != 'pending'
        API-->>U: 409 Conflict ("item is not pending")
    end
    API->>PG: resolve_provider_config("ingest", vault_id)  %% I6 - never hardcode
    alt no ingest provider configured
        API-->>U: 409 Conflict ("no ingest provider configured")
    end

    Note over API: Derive skeleton - title from proposed_title, type from proposed_page_type (or heuristic §5.2), dir from type_subdir(final_type)
    API->>L: run_orchestrated_loop(single-page-target prompt, provider, max_iter, token_budget)  %% I6/I7 - bounded
    Note over L: Same bounded analyze→generate→validate→retry loop as the main ingest path (ADR-0009)
    loop iteration = 1..max_iter
        L->>P: generate page titled title of type type grounded in vault context and rationale
        P-->>L: WikiPage (or loop exhausted)
    end

    alt WikiPage produced (or fallback via _ensure_source_summary)
        L->>PG: INSERT ingest_runs{total_tokens, total_cost_usd, route=orchestrated} (I7 - 1 USD anomaly check)
        L-->>API: WikiPage
        API->>FS: write_wiki_page(page, origin_source)  %% I1 - single incremental write seam
        Note over API: persist_metadata → upsert_vector → append_log → bump_version (ONCE) → wikilinks → update_index
        API->>PG: bump data_version by 1
        API->>PG: UPDATE review_items SET status=created, resolution=created, created_page_id=new_id, reviewed_at=now(), reviewed_by=web-ui
        API-->>U: 201 ReviewItem (status=created, created_page_id set)
        Note over API,R: Fire-and-forget - trigger sweep so sibling proposals this new page satisfies are closed
        API-)R: sweep_reviews(vault_id)
    else generation failed (loop converged=False or provider error)
        Note over API: item status stays 'pending' - no partial write
        API-->>U: 502 ("page generation failed - item left pending, retry or skip")
    end

    %% Skip action (unchanged from ADR-0025 contract)
    Note over U,API: User clicks Skip - no page generated, item closed immediately
    U->>API: POST /review/queue/{id}/skip
    API->>PG: UPDATE review_items SET status=skipped, resolution=skipped, reviewed_at=now(), reviewed_by=web-ui
    API-->>U: 200 ReviewItem (status=skipped)

    %% Deep Research action (topic now from proposed_title / rationale, not pre_generated_query)
    Note over U,API: User clicks Deep Research - delegates to F10 loop (ADR-0024)
    U->>API: POST /review/queue/{id}/deep-research
    alt SEARXNG_URL not set
        API-->>U: 503 ("SEARXNG_URL not configured")
    end
    API->>PG: derive topic = proposed_title ?? rationale (first line) ?? page.title
    API->>PG: INSERT deep_research_runs{topic, vault_id, ...} (ADR-0024 §3)
    API->>PG: UPDATE review_items SET status=deep_researched, resolution=researched, deep_research_run_id=run_id
    API-->>U: 202 {review_item_id, run_id}

    %% Manual sweep
    Note over U,API: Operator triggers explicit sweep (testing / housekeeping)
    U->>API: POST /review/queue/sweep?vault_id=vault
    API->>R: sweep_reviews(vault_id)  %% same function as fire-and-forget path
    Note over R: Pass-1 rule-based (no LLM): resolve missing-page/duplicate where proposed_title now exists
    Note over R: Pass-2 conservative LLM (if REVIEW_SWEEP_LLM_ENABLED=true): complete() single-turn - ADR-0084- 120 s timeout - default-to-keep - never resolves confirm
    R-->>API: {rule_resolved: N, llm_resolved: M, kept: K}
    API-->>U: 200 {rule_resolved, llm_resolved, kept}
